		"description": "<p><strong>Crafting Components:</strong> Shell that&rsquo;s been home to three different sea creatures</p>\n<hr class=\"a5e-rule u-my-md\">\n<p>While wearing this charm you gain a swim speed equal to your Speed, or you can break the charm to release its power, destroying it to activate one of the following effects.</p>\n<p>&bull; <strong><em>Breathe</em></strong>: Cast @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.ug1c28d5upbq19x4]{Water Breathing}.<br>&bull; <strong><em>Cure</em></strong>: Cast @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.1vo427vjnzgzb5z2]{Cure Wounds} at 3rd-level (+3 spellcasting ability modifier).<br>&bull; <strong><em>Numb</em></strong>: Cast @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.qvi9ra3gzxi3sd28]{Sleet Storm} (spell save DC 15).</p>\n<p><strong>Curse</strong>. Releasing the charm&rsquo;s power attracts the attention of a marid or water elemental who seeks you out to recruit you for a task.</p>",
